SELECT b0."Id", b0."IdentityGuid", b0."Name", p."Id", p."BuyerId", p."Alias", p."CardHolderName", p."CardNumber", p."CardTypeId", p."Expiration"
FROM (
    SELECT b."Id", b."IdentityGuid", b."Name"
    FROM ordering.buyers AS b
    WHERE b."IdentityGuid" = @__identity_0
    LIMIT 2
) AS b0
LEFT JOIN ordering.paymentmethods AS p ON b0."Id" = p."BuyerId"
ORDER BY b0."Id"
